      • removeRoom

        public void removeRoom​(java.lang.String roomId)
        Method used for removing a room, by calling the corresponding method from the model. After method has completed, the list of rooms is updated to reflect the changes. If an exception is caught during this process, the error-label will be updated accordingly.
        Parameters:
        roomId - the id of the room to be deleted.
